<text><body>
<lb n="0781a16"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0781a17"/>
<lb n="0781a18"/><head type="no">No. 1182 [No. 1181, cf. No. 1191]</head>
<lb n="0781a19"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0781010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】承德元年寫東寺三密藏本</note>曼殊<note n="0781011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">室＝師【甲】</note><app n="0781011"><lem>室</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">師</rdg></app>利菩薩&CB00057;藏中一字&CB00057;
<lb n="0781a20"/>王經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0781a21"/>
<lb n="0781a22"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0781012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大）＋唐【元】</note><app n="0781012"><lem>唐</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">大唐</rdg></app>三藏法師義淨奉　制<note n="0781013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（第二）＋譯【元】</note><app n="0781013"><lem>譯</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">第二譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0781a23"/><div1 type="jing"><p>爾時釋迦牟尼佛。在淨居天<note n="0781014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上於天〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781014"><lem>上。於天</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>眾中跏
<lb n="0781a24"/>趺正念。普觀大眾而告之曰。汝諸天子。當至
<lb n="0781a25"/>心聽曼殊室利童子微妙之行。所謂壇場神
<lb n="0781a26"/>&CB00057;作法。所須療病護身。第一祕密最上&CB00057;
<lb n="0781a27"/>心。一切如來所共宣說咸皆稱歎。是大&CB00057;王。
<lb n="0781a28"/>若有善男子善女人。能誦此&CB00057;者。則為受持
<lb n="0781a29"/>一切神&CB00057;。汝諸天眾。此大&CB00057;王無能違者。假
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1182.0781b" n="0781b"/>
<lb n="0781b01"/>使曼殊室利童子菩薩摩訶薩。此&CB00057;亦能隨
<lb n="0781b02"/>心自在引攝將來。令使現前為作眾事。況復
<lb n="0781b03"/>諸餘菩薩。世出世間所有神&CB00057;。一切障礙悉
<lb n="0781b04"/>皆<note n="0781015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔除〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781015"><lem>除</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>遣。有大勇猛有大威力。神驗第一。諸
<lb n="0781b05"/>&CB00057;中上一字中尊。此之一字悉能成就一切
<lb n="0781b06"/>事業。悉能圓滿所有善法。常在一切世出世
<lb n="0781b07"/>間。&CB00057;術之上不可毀壞。是一切佛心。悉能滿
<lb n="0781b08"/>足所有求願。汝諸天眾。咸皆一心聽此不可
<lb n="0781b09"/>思議具大威力最上神&CB00057;。即說&CB00057;曰。</p>
<lb n="0781b10"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0781016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵上三本俱有梵字</note>唵叱洛呬焰<note place="inline">此有四字總成一字是故梵漢二體俱<note n="0781017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">存＝在之【甲】</note><app n="0781017"><lem>存</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">在之</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0781b11"/><p>汝等天眾。此是一切祕密中勝一字&CB00057;王。一
<lb n="0781b12"/>切有情無敢違者。一切鬼神不敢親近。一切
<lb n="0781b13"/>諸<note n="0781018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781018"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>為吉祥事。一切&CB00057;中最能成立隨意所
<lb n="0781b14"/>為。一切世間作大尊勝。於求財者有大自在
<lb n="0781b15"/>能令富盛。諸瞋恚中此<note n="0781019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝念【甲】</note><app n="0781019"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">念</rdg></app>慈善。於諸含識
<lb n="0781b16"/>悲愍為性。有違逆者皆悉順從。要<note n="0781020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔而〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781020"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>言之。
<lb n="0781b17"/>凡有所為悉皆成就。縱不作法入壇場等直
<lb n="0781b18"/>爾誦持。手觸彼時即便隨意。&CB00057;衣著時。人皆
<lb n="0781b19"/>愛樂見者歡喜若&CB00057;齒木用揩齒時。齒<note n="0781021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔疼〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781021"><lem>疼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>即
<lb n="0781b20"/><note n="0781022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差＝瘥【宋】＊，著【甲】＊</note><note n="0781022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差＝瘥【宋】＊，＝著【甲】＊</note><app n="0781022"><lem>差</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">瘥</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">著</rdg></app>。若患眼時。取先陀婆鹽研之為<note n="0781023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">末＝粖【宋】【元】，&CB00331;【甲】</note><note n="0781023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">末＝粖【宋】【元】，＝&CB00331;【甲】</note><app n="0781023"><lem>末</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">粖</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00331;</rdg></app>。&CB00057;七
<lb n="0781b21"/>遍已少置眼中。其痛便止。若患耳者。取象馬
<lb n="0781b22"/>糞聚上地<note n="0781024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">菌＝園【甲】</note><app n="0781024"><lem>菌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">園</rdg></app>。并<note n="0781025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">苣&CB01091;＝巨勝【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0781025"><lem>苣&CB01091;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【甲】" resp="Taisho">巨勝</rdg></app>油先陀婆鹽。各取少
<lb n="0781b23"/>許&CB00057;之七遍。一處研使碎絞取汁煖之。<note n="0781026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">渧＝滴【三】</note><note n="0781026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">渧＝滴【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781026"><lem>渧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">滴</rdg></app>耳
<lb n="0781b24"/>孔中其痛便止。若有女人。將產之時。被胎所
<lb n="0781b25"/>惱腹中結痛不能疾出。取阿吒留灑根或牛
<lb n="0781b26"/>膝根。取無蟲水磨擣令碎。&CB00057;之七遍塗在臍
<lb n="0781b27"/>下。即能易出。若人被射。箭鏃入身不能出者。
<lb n="0781b28"/>可取<note n="0781027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陳酥＝練蘇【甲】</note><app n="0781027"><lem>陳酥</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">練蘇</rdg></app>&CB00057;一百八遍。令彼飲之其鏃便出。
<lb n="0781b29"/>若患宿食不消。腹中結痛<note n="0781028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（&CB00057;）＋上【甲】</note><app n="0781028"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00057;上</rdg></app>變下瀉<note n="0781029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03659;＝霍【三】</note><note n="0781029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03659;＝霍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781029"><lem>&CB03659;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">霍</rdg></app>亂
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1182.0781c" n="0781c"/>
<lb n="0781c01"/>畏死者。可取烏鹽或先陀婆鹽或諸雜鹽類。
<lb n="0781c02"/>&CB00057;之七遍。研<note n="0781030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔碎〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781030"><lem>碎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>煖水令服便<app type="＊" source="0781022"><lem>差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">著</rdg></app>。或復苦痢
<lb n="0781c03"/>不能斷者。取橘柚根及榠樝根。磨擣&CB00057;之七
<lb n="0781c04"/>遍。和水服之即<app type="＊" source="0781022"><lem>差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">著</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0781c05"/><p>若<note n="0781031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝有【明】</note><app n="0781031"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">有</rdg></app>石女無產生法。欲求男女者。應取阿說
<lb n="0781c06"/>健陀根。以<note n="0781032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酥＝蘇【甲】＊</note><app n="0781032"><lem>酥</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">蘇</rdg></app>熟煎<note n="0781033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">擣＝禱【甲】</note><app n="0781033"><lem>擣</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">禱</rdg></app>之令碎。和黃牛乳&CB00057;
<lb n="0781c07"/>二十五遍。待彼女人身淨之時令飲其藥。<note n="0781034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妻＝毒【甲】</note><app n="0781034"><lem>妻</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">毒</rdg></app>
<lb n="0781c08"/>莫犯他男。夫莫犯他女。未久之間即便有娠。
<lb n="0781c09"/>或復女人斷緒無子。<note n="0781035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝住【甲】</note><app n="0781035"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>三五年或復多年。或
<lb n="0781c10"/>被他<note n="0781036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禁＝梵【甲】</note><app n="0781036"><lem>禁</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">梵</rdg></app>&CB00057;或由<note n="0781037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">厭＝&CB01679;【三】</note><note n="0781037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">厭＝&CB01679;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781037"><lem>厭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB01679;</rdg></app>禱。或因諸病或他所惱
<lb n="0781c11"/>或遭毒藥。遇此惡緣遂無子息者。應取少許
<lb n="0781c12"/>孔雀尾。安<note n="0781038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陳＝練【甲】</note><app n="0781038"><lem>陳</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">練</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0781032"><lem>酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蘇</rdg></app>中箭之數沸。研令相得。投
<lb n="0781c13"/>少石蜜量如<note n="0781039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">棗＝朿【甲】</note><app n="0781039"><lem>棗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">朿</rdg></app>許。&CB00057;二<note n="0781040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十＋（二十）【甲】</note><app n="0781040"><lem>十</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">十二十</rdg></app>七遍服之令盡。
<lb n="0781c14"/>於後七日中日日常以石蜜和乳。每&CB00057;七遍
<lb n="0781c15"/>飲之。女身清淨諸病皆<note n="0781041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差＝瘥【宋】＊</note><app n="0781041"><lem>差</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">瘥</rdg></app>即便有娠。若有女
<lb n="0781c16"/>人月水不息。應以阿藍部根或以藍根<note n="0781042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝或【甲】</note><app n="0781042"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">或</rdg></app>握
<lb n="0781c17"/>擣之。和乳熟煎&CB00057;一百八遍服之即<app type="＊" source="0781041"><lem>差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>。若患
<lb n="0781c18"/>頭痛者。應以烏羽&CB00057;之七遍。掃<note n="0781043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拂痛＝拂病【三】，&CB01673;痛【甲】</note><note n="0781043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拂痛＝拂病【宋】【元】【明】，＝&CB01673;痛【甲】</note><app n="0781043"><lem>拂痛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">拂病</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB01673;痛</rdg></app>處即便
<lb n="0781c19"/>永<app type="＊" source="0781041"><lem>差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>。若人患瘧。或一日二日三日四日發
<lb n="0781c20"/>者。或常熱病或暫時熱病。應以乳粥和<app type="＊" source="0781032"><lem>酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蘇</rdg></app>&CB00057;
<lb n="0781c21"/>一百八遍。食之即<app type="＊" source="0781041"><lem>差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>。若人被他<note n="0781044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">厭＝&CB01679;【三】【甲】</note><note n="0781044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">厭＝&CB01679;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0781044"><lem>厭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB01679;</rdg></app>魅<note n="0781045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠱＝蟲【三】</note><note n="0781045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蠱＝蟲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781045"><lem>蠱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">蟲</rdg></app>毒
<lb n="0781c22"/>所中。應作反緣心。&CB00057;自<app><lem>己</lem><rdg wit="【大】">已</rdg></app>面一百八遍。<note n="0781046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">觀＝視【甲】</note><app n="0781046"><lem>觀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">視</rdg></app>彼
<lb n="0781c23"/>病人所患便<note n="0781047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差＝瘥【宋】，著【甲】</note><note n="0781047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差＝瘥【宋】，＝著【甲】</note><app n="0781047"><lem>差</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">瘥</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">著</rdg></app>。若人被邪鬼羯吒布單那等
<lb n="0781c24"/>諸鬼所著。或小兒諸病。但是一切非人所為
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1182.0782a" n="0782a"/>
<lb n="0782a01"/>共相惱者。應&CB00057;自手一百八遍。<note n="0782001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩病＝病摩【甲】</note><app n="0782001"><lem>摩病</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">病摩</rdg></app>人頭即
<lb n="0782a02"/>眾病皆<app type="＊" source="0781041"><lem>差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>。若人被蛇蠍所蜇或狂狗所傷。以
<lb n="0782a03"/>氣急吹瘡上。&CB00057;之七七遍即<app type="＊" source="0781041"><lem>差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>。若有人患癩
<lb n="0782a04"/>病瘦病者。應洗浴潔淨於閑靜處。常誦此&CB00057;
<lb n="0782a05"/>悉皆除愈。凡誦&CB00057;之人。常須遠離惡人不淨
<lb n="0782a06"/>臭穢之處不近酒肉五辛。一心受持無不驗
<lb n="0782a07"/>者。若有一日常誦一遍。能護自身。若誦二遍
<lb n="0782a08"/>能護同伴。若誦三遍能護一家。若誦四遍能
<lb n="0782a09"/>護一村。若誦五遍能護一城。若誦百遍能護
<lb n="0782a10"/>一國。若誦千遍能護四天下。以要言之略述
<lb n="0782a11"/>如是。療病護身隨時利益。若更有餘所為之
<lb n="0782a12"/>事。皆隨意作無不成就。爾時諸天大眾聞佛
<lb n="0782a13"/>說此一字&CB00057;王經已。歡喜奉行<note place="inline">若復有人志求解脫<note n="0782002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">希＋（有）【甲】</note><app n="0782002"><lem>希</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">希有</rdg></app>大利益現望
<lb n="0782a14"/>果證者當可<note n="0782003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至＝志【宋】</note><app n="0782003"><lem>至</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">志</rdg></app>心依&CB00057;藏中作大&CB00057;法廣說如經</note>。</p>
